OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWork long hours or leave,  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FMusk tells Twitter staff   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Elon Musk has told Twitter staff that  
OL,6, they must commit to working "long hours
OL,7, at high intensity" or else leave the   
OL,8, company, according to reports.         
OL,10,FIn an email to staff, the social media 
OL,11,Ffirm's new owner said workers should   
OL,12,Fagree to the pledge if they wanted to  
OL,13,Fstay, the Washington Post reported.    
OL,15,FThose who do not sign up by Thursday   
OL,16,Fwill be given three months' severance  
OL,17,Fpay, Mr Musk said.                     
OL,19,FThe BBC has contacted Twitter for      
OL,20,Fcomment.                               
